{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "These people, they somehow had to-- had to show that they were women, had to prove to themselves that they were women.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But I still couldn't understand how they could fight about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And that was every time we had clothes given there was such a fight going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I-- I never went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I always went there at the last one and what was on the floor I picked it up and put it on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And I looked like a scarecrow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Everybody remembers me looking like a scarecrow because I always had on something odd which nobody wanted anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But that-- that--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there is so much I think about camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, because Willy saved my life, I-- I was-- had this ambivalent feeling with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- I didn't hate him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't love him, but I didn't hate him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I wanted to put that down because I-- it will come back in another way later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were brought there to work in a factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were working in the second-largest munitions factory that was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a factory by Dynamit Nobel AG.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, oddly enough, it was-- in these days it was in where we are talking about is not by name.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The man was Frick, and I don't know whether the name Frick means anything to you, but Frick was the one who owned this factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and this factory produced-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because-- because Frick later on refused to pay anything to the slave laborers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, this-- this factory produced grenades and mines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I was put on the grenade production, and I was-- and we had a group of people, a group of women, who did not quite agree of helping the German war effort.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
